{"tid":596704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老母乜都有藉口 好垃圾","createTime":"2018-03-18T02:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T02:55:11.000Z","uid":155038,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2bb3716ce579af1a326923d7651185ea9b3418","tid":596704,"uid":155038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T02:34:02.000Z","msg":"老母4x歲，無業，日日係屋企睇電視玩電話，得閒做下家務（洗衫拖地少煮飯），無了。<br />\n<br />\n咁佢過呢d生活係佢既事，無問題。但其他野一概有藉口。<br />\n<br />\n佢話自己肥，叫佢跑下步，「個心跳得好快，好似就死」<br />\n<br />\n佢話唔識打中文字，叫佢學下，「要細個學先學到」<br />\n<br />\n佢去旅行，搭巴士要拉喼行二十分鐘，「似你後生仔咩，點拉喼行二十分鐘」<br />\n<br />\n朝朝起身話就自己腰酸背痛呢到病果到痛（心理病）<br />\n<br />\n有次返工唔開心同佢呻兩句，佢「返工已經無壓力，留係屋企先最多野煩最大壓力」<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢無財政壓力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5854db6a1478bd2c800a79f2d472fec4c7cf2985","tid":596704,"uid":23975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"好似典型廢老: 拎老綜，住公屋，好大壓力！"},{"pid":"e854d8996d95be549938e61798236ca8768baf39","tid":596704,"uid":155038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"仲有未講<br />\n<br />\n我自己搵2萬頭，之前比8000家用。有兄弟姊妹，加埋比萬幾家用啦。<br />\n<br />\n仆佢個街，比完家用發現屋企成日有幾百蚊既六合彩飛、澳門船飛，原來攞晒d錢去賭。<br />\n<br />\n叫佢唔好晒錢問六合彩，「你唔好睇死我，終有一日我會發達」<br />\n<br />\n有次佢係澳門輸到打返黎問我借錢賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慶過火屎，之後剩比2000家用，直到現在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ec3256141a8f8fb216dc9aab64a52d269c77cb","tid":596704,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"廢老 食塞米 扮晒蟹既屎忽鬼"}]}